Qf3 { Now Black can't put the Rook on c8 fast enough. } 10... Nbd7 11. O-O-O
Rc8 12. Nd5
{ White has the advantage and also an easy game. We want to go g2-g4 and  12...h4  won't stop us, we will simply play  13.g3  . }
