Rxe6 { The next moves are forced. } 27... Rxg6 28. Rxe7+ Qxe7 29. Bxe7 Rg1
{ Black is lucky to have the ...Bc6-b5 threat. } 30. Rxc6 Kxc6 31. Ke2
{ The position should be drawn but with the Bishop pair, White keeps some practical winning chances. }
