15... Qh4+
{ After both  15...Qxf4  16.Nd5+  and @@StartFEN@@rnb2b1r/2Nnkppp/p2pp3/6q1/PPBN1P2/2p5/4Q1PP/R3K1R1 b Q - 0 15@@EndFEN@@  15...Qg6  16.Bd3  , the Queen is lost. }
16. g3 Qh3 17. Ncxe6 { In view of  17...fxe6  18.Bxe6  , Black can resign. } *

