{ Now the light-squared Bishop will become a problem for Black, just like in the French. }
14... Qa5 { 14...b5?!  15.Ne2  would only make things easier. } 15. Qf2
{ White keeps control over the dark squares and is ready to bring the Knight to d4 with a small but long-term advantage. }
