7. h3 { Preventing ...Bc8-g4. } 7... e6 8. Nc3 Ne7 9. b3
{ We will bring the Bishop to a3 and shift the Knight a4. Black's position is already difficult, even if the c5-Pawn will be saved, the light-squared Bishop will be left without any perspectives. }
