25. Nb1 { A new plan. Previously, only  25.Nb3  has been tried. } 25... Ne8 26.
Nc3 b4 27. Na2 b3 { This is one square too far. } 28. Nc1 Bd8 29. Ba7
{ The Bishop gets out at the last moment. We will collect the Pawn,  29...Ba4  30.Bc4  , and then consolidate our pieces. This won't be easy to convert, perhaps not possible at all, but remember we are playing against humans, not machines. }
