24... g6 25. Rd5 { This time, we are threatening Rc5. } 25... Kg7
{ 26.Rc5?!  will be now met with  26...Qxa3  . } 26. Rd6
{ Almost surgical accuracy but sometimes that's required from us. White is threatening Qf6+ or Rf6. }
26... Qxf3 27. Rg3 Qf1+ 28. Kb2
{ The Rook is coming to c3 and then to the 7th rank. Black is helpless. } *

