{ All of it is forced since Black has no other alternatives. } 20. Rxe5+ Kd7
21. Rxe3 { Threatening Rd1+, which, once again, limits Black's options. } 21...
Bc5 22. Rd1+ Kc6 23. Nd4+
{ After  23...Kb6  24.c3  , White has an extra Pawn and a better endgame. } *

