{ Let Black take the Pawn, development is more important to us. } 9... b4 10.
Ne2 Qxe4 { 10...Bb7  11.O-O-O  Nf6  12.f3  would transpose. } 11. Rg1
{ The Queen is pretty exposed on e4, but that goes without saying. } 11... Qc4
{ The main move in the position. } 12. Ng3 Qc7
