{ White is easily better here. First, we need to push the Queen back. } 10. g3
Qc7 11. e5 Ng8 12. Ne4 { White's initiative is too strong. } 12... Nh6 13. Nd6+
Bxd6 14. exd6 Qa5+ { 14...Qxd6  15.Bxg7  . } 15. b4 Qg5 16. Bg2
{ We will castle short. It's difficult to talk about compensation and White practically has a winning position here. }
