{ Once again, it's a bad idea − in the @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/1p1p1ppp/p3p3/8/3NP3/8/PPP2PPP/RNBQKB1R w KQkq - 0 5@@EndFEN@@  5.Bd3  Bc5  line, Black gains a tempo thanks to attacking the Knight. }
