1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 e6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 Bb4
{ There is an impressive list of games in the database by Baadur Jobava in this line. Although knowing the style of the Georgian grandmaster, it can hardly be considered a good recommendation. }
