11... g6 12. h4 { White's attack should be unstoppable. } 12... dxe5 13. h5 f5
14. Bxf5 { The Bishop's sacrifice wins by force. } 14... exf5 15. Qc4+ Kg7 16.
hxg6 f4 { 16...hxg6  17.Bh6+  . } 17. Rxh7+ Kxg6 18. Rh4
{ White is threatening Qe4+ but also the simple O-O-O. Black is too badly developed to resist. }
