{ White is much better. We want to push a4-a5, which is a common resource. With the Pawn on a5, Black will have to consider a5xb6 or a5-a6 all the time, which adds constant pressure. After that, we can do the same thing on the Kingside: advance the h-Pawn and activate the Rook. }
