10... O-O 11. Ne4 exf4 12. Nxd6
{ You would probably agree that White has the initiative, but what about White having an almost winning advantage? After  12...Qc7  13.Qh5  b6  14.Bc4  , Black's position is already critical.  14...Be6  15.Bxe6  fxe6  16.Rhe1  and both  16...Qe7  and  16...e5  will be met with  17.Qf3  . }
