18. Nf3 { Sacrificing that Pawn is our only way to fight for an advantage. }
18... Bxe5 19. Nxe5 Qxe5 20. Bd2
{ White has nice compensation for the Pawn. The black King is not safe in the center and it won't be easy for Black to solve this problem. We can bring the Rooks to e1 and d1, hoping for some tactics in the center. }
