{ For today's engines, this is easy, White is completely winning. For humans, it took a while to figure that out − almost two hundred games in a database! }
20... f6 { Taking g5 under control. } 21. exf6 Qc7
{ Bringing the Queen back as quickly as possible but now the black King will be naked. }
22. fxg7 Qxg7 23. Ne5 { There is a simple yet deadly threat: Rf1-f3. } 23...
Rf5 24. Qh4 Qf6 25. Qg3+ Qg7
{ 25...Kf8  would be met with  26.Qa3+!  Kg8  27.Rf3  . } 26. Qe1
{ Our Queen will no longer be bothered so we are free to proceed with Rf1-f3. Black is completely lost. }
