24... Qf5 { The Queen takes an eye on the c2-Pawn, stopping 25.Qa7. } 25. Rb8+
{ As mentioned earlier, there were two threats. } 25... Kd7 26. Qa7+ Bc7
{ For this reason, the immediate 24.Rb8+ didn't work. What has changed? } 27.
Kxc3 { Quite a lot! ;-@@EndBracket@@ Black can resign. } *

