{ Let's see what happens if Black takes the bait. } 34. Ng6+
{ The first surprise. After  34...fxg6  35.f7  , White is completely winning. }
34... Kg8
{ The Bishop can't really be taken since after  35.Nxh4  Re1  , Black is fine. }
35. Re7 { Second surprise and probably the last one. Black is losing a piece. }
