{ 26...Be6  is easy.  27.Bxe6  fxe6  28.Nxe6  Qe7  29.Qd5  and White wins the piece back, obtaining a winning position. }
27. Qe4 Bf5 28. Nxf7+
{ This has to be seen @@StartBracket@@known@@EndBracket@@ in advance. } 28...
