{ Black wants to trade the light-squared Bishop with ...Bc8-a6. The plan is strategically sound, but it takes time, and just a quick glance at the Kingside makes it clear: it is not a good moment for time-consuming operations.   4...Qd7  5.h4  b6  transposes. }
