{ Let's just ignore it. White's superior developoment will be a decisive factor. }
8... Nc6 9. O-O
{ White has finished development while Black hasn't really started yet. We can further improve the position with c2-c3 and then either something like a2-a3 and b2-b4 or simply d4-d5 should work. }
