6. Be3 Qb6 { This looks so wrong... } 7. Nd2 e6
{ 7...Qxb2?  8.Rb1  Qxa2  9.Rxb7  is just winning for White. The disproportion between the two sides is too big. }
8. Nb3 { What is Black's Bishop doing on d7?! } 8... Na6
{ Quite original, but by no means sufficient. } 9. h5 c5 10. dxc5 Nxc5 11. f4
{ We will move the Queen to d2 and castle long. Black is struggling to finish development and even if that will be achieved, the position is still and with no perspectives. }
