{ Because Black is a Pawn up, we can't say that White is winning but I will evaluate it as 'White is much better'. After  17...Be7  we can go  18.Qe2  , preparing Rd1-d3, Be3-g5, or Nf3-g5 − basically all kinds of cool attacking moves. }
