{ Let's see how L'Ami's idea works with the a2-a3 and ...a7-a5 inclusion. } 17.
Qxf4 Rh6 18. Ng5 f6 19. exf6 Rxf6 20. Bxf6 gxf6 21. Nf3 e5 22. Qh6
{ Black doesn't have ...Qb6-b4+ @@StartBracket@@which would normally be the move@@EndBracket@@. Moreover, Black's Queen is not protected. }
22... O-O-O 23. O-O
{ White is threatening Nf3xe5, which gives Black no time for ...Rd8-g8. } 23...
Qd6 24. Qxh5 Rg8 25. Rae1
{ This is not good compensation for Black. We want to move the Queen to h6 and then perhaps bring the Rook to e3.  25...Bh3  can be met with  26.Ng5! }
