{ The position resembles the Caro-Kann Defense with one big difference: Black hasn't managed to develop the light-squared Bishop. }
7... Nb6 8. g4
{ White's aggressive play is justified. We didn't want Black to play ...h7-h5 followed by ...Bc8-f5. }
8... g6
